	Yukon fuzz-rock power trio Electric Lemonade pairs big feelings with an audacious sound. Drawing from influences like Alabama Shakes and Soundgarden, Electric Lemonade fuse grunge-soaked riffs with stories of queer desire, mental health, and fractured friendships, music built to move through and feel deeply.
