<http://www.spektrix.com/yukonartscentre/event/65401ARRMBSGBRKRMPJDLPDLGHVCMRJJP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Guild Hall Comedy Night";
  schema:description """
	All local comedy at the Guild Hall this March, hosted by the one and only Brenda Barnes! Come on out and enjoy the salty stylings of Steph Aubé. Welcome back the delightful Felix O’Laney and Ray MacDonald to the Guild stage. Revel in the cheeky and irreverent Ivanna Fitswell and newcomer Frances Kitson. Celebrate spring with these hilarious Yukon comedians! Thank you to our sponsors: Government of Yukon, Lotteries Yukon, City of Whitehorse, Whitehorse Motors, Kilrich Building Centre, Yukon Brewing, SPK Home Construction Ltd, Crêperie La Petite Maison and Air North
""";
