  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "La tournée d’humour des Rendez-vous de la Francophonie";
  schema:description """
	5:00–7:00 p.m. — The kickoff reception for Les Rendez-vous de la Francophonie 2026, taking place in the lobby. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Guests are invited to enjoy pre-show drinks and appetizers provided by Compadres Burritos. A cash bar will be available on site. Complimentary non-alcoholic drinks will be offered.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>7:00 p.m. — Doors open for the show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>8:00 p.m. — Show begins. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>9:30 p.m. — Show ends.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Please be advised that both the kickoff reception and the stand-up show will be presented exclusively in French.</span>
""";
